tutorialEntries:
Our first type of "Loop Statement" is the while-Statement:
while(<condition>) {
	<consequent>
}

Inside your while-Statement you need this:
	if (<knight name>.canMove()){
		<knight name>.move();
	}

else if (<knight name>.targetsCell(EXIT)){
	<knight name>.useItem();
}
else {
	<knight name>.turn(RIGHT);
}
